features: ⚡[What You Get]: Our 3 pack 6ft 60W PD USB C to USB C fast charging cables come with a 12-month warranty and 24/7 customer service. If you have any other questions, please contact us, and we will solve your issue within 24 hours.
⚡[Wide Compatibility]: Our USB C cables are compatible with most type c port devices, for iPhone 15/15 Pro/15 Plus/15 Pro Max, Samsung Galaxy S23 S23+ S23 Ultra/ S22/S21 Ultra, Google Pixel.

⚡[Durability and Quality]: High quality TPE material makes our USB C cable durable and strong while remaining flexible and tangle-free. Prevents the connector from breaking easily, and it can withstand up to 30,000 bends.
⚡[Safe and Stable]: Safe, tough durable. With advanced connectors, quality is guaranteed, preventing breakage. Regulates current, boosting battery and device life, protecting from unstable voltage.

⚡[60W Fast Charging]: Our USB C to USB C cable supports up to 60W safe and fast charging. The sync data speed is up to 480Mbps. It efficiently charges your devices, such as laptops, smartphones, tablets, and other USB C port devices, in a shorter amount of time compared to other cables.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on April 5, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Fast charging, excellent value for money, and the cords all work great! I love how easily you can wind and store them without worrying about the cable cracking. Just took mine on a couple of cross-country flights, and I was able to keep the majority of the cord rubberbanded in the middle while I plugged my phone into charge and then unwind it to easily use my phone in the hotel bed. I love that you get three of them. I have one in each room in my house at all times. 100% recommend these!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on April 6, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Excellent charging cables!
reviews.reviewText: These are the best cables I've bought in a while. I use them on my iPhone as well as my iPad, they charge fast and reliably. They're well made, I like that they're covered in braided nylon which makes them more durable. The length is great because they easily reach an outlet no matter how far away I'm sitting. I can't say enough good things, buy them you won't regret it!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on March 21, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Long enough reach wherever I need it and feel durable for the long time use
reviews.reviewText: I used have a short iPhone charger was very inconvenient for me. But this one is nice and long and much sturdier than the one used to have. The longer cords are great for my dining table where I spend a lot time studying. I am very pleased with the charger. I like the fact the a three pack of 10 ft cables are in the package so that I can use other for my iPad. And the price was very very reasonable. I ma very glad that I brought these cords to place in different location.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 26, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Great for the price!
reviews.reviewText: Out of the 3, I still currently use a a functioning cord and that's only because I lost one and the other stopped working after a couple months. Either way, these are still pretty good quality and durable. I think they are great for the price!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 20, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars USB on one end
reviews.reviewText: I bought these for work vehicles. We drive E-450's and they do not have a type C connector, just usb ports. We use iPhones to clock in and out and for communication, so the cables that came with the phone could not be used. These are great, they're a good length and seem very sturdy so far. And they charge the phones great! And a great price for a multi pack! We are very happy with these cables. I recommend.
